metadata.name: Majesty #1/1
metadata.description:
Hash Directors presents JUUC - The anonymous poet.
His painterly style and approach to thematics and vision is a truly unique style that sets him apart from the rest of the new generation of AI artists. Every piece is composed and presented as a classical oil painting, and the mysterious thematics and world he invites us in is an enigma waiting to unfold. The main perspective is not only guided thru the color orange but also by hidden elements in the artworks.
Pleased to introduce: JUUC
